-- Bed Bath reports lower 4th-qtr net income
-- 
-- Wed Apr 9, 2008 4:36pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/04/09/us-bedbathbeyond-results-idUSWNAS727920080409

 

 LOS ANGELES  (Reuters) - Home goods retailer Bed Bath & Beyond Inc ( BBBY.O ) posted lower quarterly profit on Wednesday as the nationwide housing slump continued to weigh on sales. 

 Fourth-quarter net profit fell to $172.9 million, or 66 cents per share, from $205.8 million, or 72 cents a year ago. (Reporting by  Alexandria Sage ; editing by Jeffrey Benkoe)